REFERRED TO CRIME VICTIMS, CRIME AND CORRECTION

Title: Relates to registration requirements applicable to certain sex offenders who are transient
Summary: Provides registration requirements applicable to level three sex offenders and sexual predators who are transient.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the correction law, in relation to registration requirements applicable to certain sex offenders who are transient
